{"type": "article", "id": 21698, "title": "牛奶包装 by Dmitry Patsukevich", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-02T07:34:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 70, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104200Ytquiw9Mc8zODKL6.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是白俄罗斯的设计师 Dmitry Patsukevich 做的牛奶瓶概念设计，他将瓶盖做成牛奶洒开的状态，一个凝固的瞬间，仿佛瓶中的牛奶要喷出来，也吸引人们上去触摸。特别在于他并不将波浪做的有规则，而是有水珠的感觉，增加了一份自然真实。牛奶瓶是传统的样式，通体白色，只有少量的文字，像是将牛奶也凝固起来了。这个设计目前还是一个概念。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104158LdGcD1FWTphAfkYr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104159mguKHJZRE0PU4rY6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104159U8dXbBml75HzMojf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}